snippet.title: Marry Him If You Dare | 미래의 선택
snippet.description:
(SUB : ENG / MAL / VIE)
Marry Him If You Dare l 미래의 선택 
🕘 Every Sunday at 9:00 PM (Seoul, UTC+9) airing🤍

#Marryhimifyoudare #미래의선택 #DiaMencintaimuJikaKamuBerani #HãyCướiAnhẤyNếuBạnDám

Life is full of choices. Should I keep working at this job or quit?
What kind of work should I do to live well? Can I like this man or not?
Life is made up of all these choices, and each person's life is determined by them. In this life where every day is a series of choices, wouldn't it be nice if someone from the future appeared to make decisions and help you? This drama begins with such a bold imagination.

snippet.title: Memorials | 출사표
snippet.description:
Job seeker Gu Se-ra got fired three times in a row for pointing out what is right. Then, attracted by the $500,000 salary, she decides to run for the district representative and then to chairman election, which would pay even more if she wins. Meanwhile, Senator Jo Maeng-duk, who looks at Se-ra with disapproval, tries to make her into a figurehead chairwoman. Realizing Maeng-duk’s intentions, the demoted elite deputy director Gong-myung visits Se-ra and offers to become her secretary! The fiery-tempered Se-ra and the cool-headed Gong-myung slowly grow closer.
Wh ill S’ lif th ditit tti b hdi?
